  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/USBDriverKit\/utilities\ncrawled: 2026-03-11T11:40:20Z\n---\n\n# Utilities\n\n**API Collection**\n\nManipulate bit structures and convert integers between device- and platform-native formats.\n\n## Integer Conversion Routines\n\n- **HostToUSB16**\n- **HostToUSB32**\n- **HostToUSB64**\n- **USBToHost16**\n- **USBToHost32**\n- **USBToHost64**\n\n## Bit Manipulations\n\n- **IOUSBBit**\n- **IOUSBBitRange**\n- **IOUSBBitRange64**\n- **IOUSBBitRangePhase**\n\n## Bitrate Constants\n\n- **kIOUSB30Bitrate5Gbps**\n- **kIOUSB30Bitrate10Gbps**\n- **kIOUSB32Bitrate20Gbps**\n\n## USB Specifications\n\n- **USB Device Descriptors**: Determine the capabilities and configuration of a device using descriptors from the USB specification.\n- **Additional Specifications**: Request information from a device and get hardware and timing information.\n- **Registry Property Names**: Search for specific keys in the device registry.\n\n",
